overview: Kamryn has recently been adopted by a single foster father, but she longs for a female presence in her life. Her foster father asks Lisey if she would be willing to fill that role. The girls bond far quicker and mroe intensely than anyone had hoped.  Aiden discovers that her new foster daughter was kicked out of her last home for inappropriate behavior with her previous foster dad. To end the problem before it starts, Aiden creats a physical bond between the whole family right away.
title: Foster Tapes 4
